nodes.text: Telos Dock module 126 was located on Citadel Station of Telos IV. It had three major docking bays; one belonged to the Telos Security Force, one belonged to the Ithorian's restoration project and the last belonged to Czerka Corporation. Each had a receptionist and a docking administrator.

When Brianna stole the Ebon Hawk from its hangar and brought it to the Telosian Jedi Academy, the hangar that belonged to the Telos Security Force was temporarily locked down pending an investigation.
